"1 tablespoon butter","4  medium Gala apples, cored and cut into (1/4-inch-thick) wedges","2  slices applewood-smoked bacon, chopped","20 ounces small cipollini onions, peeled","1/3 cup fat-free, less-sodium chicken broth","2 tablespoons cider vinegar","1 1/2 teaspoons fresh thyme leaves","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","  Thyme sprigs (optional)"